compiler_mono_instrapp_assc: Lemma instrapp_assc: forall l1 l2 l3,l1 ++ l2 ++ l3 = (l1 ++ l2) ++ l3.
compiler_mono_correct_compilation_strong: Lemma correct_compilation_strong:forall  (l : listinstr) (e : exp) (s: listnat), (@eq listnat (execIs (instrapp (compile e) l) s) (  execIs l (Natcons (evalExp e) s))).
compiler_mono_app_nil_end: Theorem app_nil_end: forall l, l = instrapp l Instrnil.
compiler_mono_correct_compilation: Theorem correct_compilation:forall e,(execIs (compile e) Natnil) =(Natcons (evalExp e) Natnil).
